data.description: Welcome to rural Bixby! Nestled in a serene rural setting on 1.11 acres of land, this charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of tranquility and modern living. Located just minutes from Lake Bixhoma, outdoor enthusiasts will delight in the proximity to nature's beauty. Step inside to discover a freshly painted interior adorned with updates throughout. The master bathroom has been tastefully renovated, providing a luxurious retreat, while the kitchen boasts granite countertops, stylish tile flooring, and new light fixtures, creating a space that's as functional as it is inviting. Entertain guests in the vaulted living room, where soaring ceilings enhance the sense of space and light, or head upstairs to the additional game room, perfect for family gatherings or quiet relaxation. With its blend of modern amenities, rural charm, and proximity to outdoor recreation, this home is sure to capture your heart. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours! Schedule a viewing today
